skoro do kraja.

704
01:15:42,805 --> 01:15:44,739
Hvala ti. Tome, slušaj,

705
01:15:44,774 --> 01:15:46,800
klinac Džek,
on ju je video.

706
01:15:46,844 --> 01:15:49,904
